# Financial Risk Risk Charge Asset Impact Amount

## identifier
de13254

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of the impact on the asset risk charge arising from the failure of a reinsurance counterparty. The amount reported must be after the aggregation formula is applied.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=FinancialRisk.RiskChargeAssetImpact.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.17
- period=instant
